# Cursor MCP Configuration for Cipher

## MCP Server Settings
Use the Cipher MCP server with aggregator mode for enhanced capabilities.

## Available Tools
When Cipher is running in aggregator mode, you have access to:
- File operations (read, write, edit)
- Memory operations (store, search, retrieve)
- Reasoning and reflection tools
- All filesystem operations

## Connection
Ensure Cipher is running before using MCP features:
```
start_cipher.bat
```